Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:39.97,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,All pirates who seek One Piece\Nstrive to reach the second half of the Grand Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:42.57,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The place called the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:51.27,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,However, the only one who ever conquered that ocean\Nwas the Pirate King, Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.26,0:02:57.61,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The New World has killed\Nthe dreams and ambitions of countless pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:03.45,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,And now, the boy who ate the Gomu Gomu Fruit\Nand became a rubber man,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:07.20,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy and his crew\Nare going to challenge that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.73,0:03:11.29,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.19,0:03:20.75,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,After a fierce battle, the Straw Hat Pirates\Nhave finally entered the New World,{cp from 592}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.75,0:03:23.27,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,the strongest sea, ruled by the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:29.06,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The crew has landed on Punk Hazard,\Nan island split between fire and ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:35.79,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,After finding out about inhumane experiments being run by the island's ruler, Master, or Caesar Clown,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.79,0:03:37.96,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Luffy went to find out what his true intentions are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.45,0:03:40.86,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, his crewmates had split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:42.16,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,What's this?{cp592}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:44.94,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,It's a footprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:49.22,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Is it an animal?\NIf it's human then they're the size of a giant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.98,0:03:52.39,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,There's something out there, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:54.38,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,They feel like monsters.  Two of 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:55.78,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,What are we going to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.22,0:03:57.30,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:04:00.06,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,Law?  Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.06,0:04:02.18,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,No, this is the snow mountain...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:03.93,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,so it's got to be them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:09.22,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,They're the hit man duo\Nwho appear in blizzards on the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.11,0:04:12.80,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,Brownbeard?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.80,0:04:17.23,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,You're on the hit list as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.76,0:04:23.65,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,You better not have hurt my crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.59,0:04:35.19,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Wha... He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:40.55,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Sorry!  They got Nami!{end cp592}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.11,0:04:51.93,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Nami's been kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:53.43,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:05:00.33,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,They were huge, but I still didn't notice them until they were right in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.33,0:05:03.14,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,First it's centaurs, now it's beastmen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.14,0:05:05.49,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,This island's crawling with weirdos.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:10.62,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Maybe they're testing us for weaknesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:15.33,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,So, they didn't come to rescue Brown-gator?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:20.00,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Their true objective seemed to be the children,\Nand our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.62,0:05:25.18,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,But it sounded like Master hired them to silence Brownbeard first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.18,0:05:26.47,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Even though they're supposed to be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.28,0:05:29.76,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Even though Brownbeard admired Master so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:34.02,Flashbacks,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,Master is the kind-hearted god of salvation.{cp from 591, which is slight rewording of 589}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.57,0:05:38.81,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Luffy, Master really is a twisted individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:44.15,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I would never let the children go back\Nto such a cruel person!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.68,0:05:48.27,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I'm also worried about Nami-Franky, who got kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.27,0:05:49.74,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Who knows what they could be doing to her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:53.70,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Yeah, we're definitely getting her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:56.19,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll leave the kids to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.19,0:05:57.83,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Hold it, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:06:01.04,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,It was my body that they took.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:03.82,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Chopper, I can't fight in this body.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:06.45,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Gimme some of those beans that you use to transform.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.45,0:06:08.05,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,The beans that make you a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:11.68,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Beans?  The Rumble Ball is a dangerous drug!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:14.06,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,It'd probably be impossible for you to control it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:18.96,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,I'll super-overcome that with fighting spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.96,0:06:20.67,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Just hurry up and gimme 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:23.07,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,We don't have time for pointless talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:25.69,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I guess we have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:32.73,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Okay, but just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.73,0:06:35.79,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Wha?!  They were in my pocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:38.54,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Well, Chopper normally carries them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:42.92,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Got it?  You can only be a monster for three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:44.67,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,After that, you won't be able to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:47.72,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,If possible, just use Kung-fu Point which I showed you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.13,0:06:54.36,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Vvvvvvvvuper!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.36,0:06:56.35,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Too soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.94,0:07:01.32,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Let's go, Franky.  This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.40,0:07:15.95,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Why are you attacking me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:24.82,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,It's no good!  I knew he'd go berserk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:28.51,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,So... what was Franky planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.24,0:07:34.61,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,After the rampage he won't be able to move,\Nso I don't think he'll be much help... at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.61,0:07:36.03,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,He's just going to be in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.34,0:07:46.02,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,I don't know where he got it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:51.90,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,but it seems that the metal man Franky\Ninstalled one of Vegapunk's lasers into his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:56.95,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,I bet I could put Vegapunk's invention to good use.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:08:04.76,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,After we dissect him and take the laser system, there'll be no other use for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.76,0:08:06.82,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Might as well throw him in the incinerator.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.82,0:08:07.84,Main,Gasmask,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:12.17,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,And can you tell me what happened\Nto those stupid Marines who came to take a ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:14.11,Main,Gasmask,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:17.18,Main,Gasmask,0,0,0,,The ambush was a success, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:18.85,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:27.85,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,What the hell is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.85,0:08:29.73,Main,Marine2,0,0,0,,A human... No, a horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:31.79,Main,Smoodge,0,0,0,,Kill 'em all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.75,0:08:35.26,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,You won't kill me so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:36.40,Main,Fanbock,0,0,0,,There's more over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:38.94,Main,Marines,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:50.38,Main,Chappe,0,0,0,,Get some!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:51.71,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,They have more coming?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:53.23,Main,Marine2,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.23,0:08:54.25,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,There's nowhere to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.63,0:09:00.19,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,Change of plans!\NWe'll put all our strength into commandeering a ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:16.67,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Captain-ch... No, Smoker-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:20.08,Main,Gasmask,0,0,0,,And now, the battle has become quite chaotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:24.74,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,So... you're saying that you can't handle it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.74,0:09:26.71,Main,Gasmask,0,0,0,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.49,0:09:31.21,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Oh, I know just the thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:39.39,Main,Gasmask,0,0,0,,Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:43.80,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,We are fighting the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.80,0:09:48.11,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,This is a perfect situation to put {\i1}him{\i0} to the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.00,0:09:53.38,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Oh, that's good.  Let's do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:10:00.17,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Immediately contact the centaurs that are out on patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.17,0:10:00.97,Main,Gasmask,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.97,0:10:04.30,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,And tell the rest of the soldiers to use this time to evacuate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.30,0:10:06.58,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,If they want to live, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.66,0:10:19.05,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Lemme go!  Lemme go, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:21.73,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,What are you perverts doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.73,0:10:23.60,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Why are you kidnapping me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:28.98,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Although I am cute, and proportioned,\Nso I understand why you would {\i1}want{\i0} to kidnap me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:31.61,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,What is this man saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:34.69,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,He must be queer.  Pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:36.92,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,But it doesn't matter what you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.92,0:10:38.86,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Luffy won't let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.86,0:10:41.50,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,You're gonna get beaten to a pulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:47.04,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,Shut up now.  People who talk too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:49.67,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,are not cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:53.84,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,But apparently,\Nthe weapon that's built into your body...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:55.26,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,is cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.26,0:10:58.67,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,And when we hand you over to Master,\Nthe reward will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:03.46,Main,Scotch+Rock,0,0,0,,{\i1}so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.54,0:11:12.27,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,But it's really cold today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.16,0:11:16.52,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,Yeah, our bodies are too cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.25,0:11:20.43,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Put some clothes on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:27.16,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,With the difference in size between us,\Nthese rifles are like cannons to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:29.14,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,We have poison-gas bullets, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.14,0:11:32.89,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,And if we don't show ourselves\Nthen there's no way to defeat us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.89,0:11:35.91,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,You got friends coming?  Of course you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.91,0:11:38.44,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,We arranged for them to come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:43.25,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,It's only natural that they'll follow our footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:52.32,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Footsteps!  Footsteps!  Man, this is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.32,0:11:55.23,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,It's so easy to see where they're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:02.59,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Hey!  Franky!  I said to cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.59,0:12:03.44,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.57,0:12:10.51,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,The footsteps disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:17.88,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:21.39,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Luffy?  And Chopper... No, that's Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.39,0:12:22.69,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:27.12,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Watch out!  There are enemies here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.95,0:12:33.34,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,Let's go, Scotch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.34,0:12:34.43,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.43,0:12:37.14,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,He must be pretty thick\Nif he didn't even notice the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.44,0:12:40.91,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,There's spikes below!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.02,0:12:43.39,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,This is almost too easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.39,0:12:45.32,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,The ice spikes will pierce him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:10.12,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:12.37,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,I guess the normal tricks won't be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.80,0:13:18.40,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,They must be the same guys from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.76,0:13:41.03,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,He disappeared again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:50.97,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,Fool, this snowy mountain is our playground.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.97,0:13:54.44,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,The entire landscape is nothing but hiding spots for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.46,0:14:05.06,Main,Rocktaur,0,0,0,,Master said that it should be around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:11.99,Main,Rocktaur,0,0,0,,That's a pretty huge building.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:13.66,Main,Gotaur,0,0,0,,A warehouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:15.99,Main,Rocktaur,0,0,0,,It's a bit unsettling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.99,0:14:17.46,Main,Rocktaur,0,0,0,,This is the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:19.25,Main,Rocktaur,0,0,0,,Okay, let's open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.38,0:14:33.53,Main,Rocktaur,0,0,0,,It's stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.53,0:14:35.17,Main,Rocktaur,0,0,0,,Hey, gimme a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.26,0:15:00.82,Main,Rocktaur,0,0,0,,Did you hear something, just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.82,0:15:02.45,Main,Centaur,0,0,0,,You probably just imagined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.45,0:15:06.97,Main,Centaur,0,0,0,,Hey, they told us not to go near this place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.97,0:15:08.99,Main,Centaur,0,0,0,,Is it really okay to open it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:13.14,Main,Rocktaur,0,0,0,,Master gave us the order to open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:15.76,Main,Rocktaur,0,0,0,,Are you doubting Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:18.46,Main,Centaur,0,0,0,,N-No, that's not it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.46,0:15:20.94,Main,Rocktaur,0,0,0,,Then quit complaining and help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:16.70,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,They're big, but they're fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:17.78,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.46,0:16:21.19,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,Dead end!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.06,0:16:31.84,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Using this technique to deflect attacks\Nin random directions isn't much good in a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:34.46,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Rayleigh taught me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.46,0:16:38.72,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Instead, turn it into a counterattack by sending\Nevery bullet back at your enemy with double power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:49.65,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:51.22,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.46,0:16:59.85,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I said cut it out, Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.43,0:17:03.33,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Why is {\i1}he{\i0}{\fscx125} {\r}the one giving you the most trouble here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.67,0:17:11.93,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,Now I'm hot and bothered.\NThey're fighting amongst themselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.93,0:17:13.28,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,They're underestimating us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.41,0:17:16.61,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Quit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.21,0:17:20.75,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,I'll show you!\NThe frozen mountain has all kinds of weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:33.13,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Look out!  The frozen summit's falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:36.27,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Luffy!  Franky!  Look up!  Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.30,0:17:40.87,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,You won't be able to dodge\Nthat block of ice after I'm done!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:43.26,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,They're attacking from the sides!  Enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.04,0:17:48.25,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,This KYP gas-bullet will knock you out instantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.25,0:17:50.38,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,Die, just like your other friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:00.97,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,He did something useful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:16.15,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Great job, Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.62,0:18:22.21,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Hey, gimme a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:38.26,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the strongest attack you've used today!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:42.89,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:48.17,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Dammit!  Sorry, Franky-Chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.17,0:18:50.74,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'll have Chopper look at your injuries later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.74,0:18:51.77,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.68,0:18:57.39,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,I thought we told you.\NThe mountain is our playground.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.39,0:18:58.95,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,It's impossible to catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:00.52,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.99,0:19:28.01,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:31.82,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,He doesn't give up.  But he can't match my reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:37.71,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,He's like a monkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:38.72,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:56.00,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Dammit.  The mountain's huge,\Nso if he gets away then it'll be impossible to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:04.89,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.48,0:20:09.12,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,Well, if it isn't Trafalgar Law, the freeloader.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:14.13,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,It's a good thing I ran into you.  Right now, Straw Hat Luffy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.97,0:20:59.04,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,What the hell do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.71,0:21:41.08,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.08,0:21:44.44,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Wait... Hey, you!  Gimme my body back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.44,0:21:45.87,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.87,0:21:46.79,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.25,0:21:52.24,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Traf!  So you saved Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:55.71,Main,Law,0,0,0,,I've been thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.79,0:22:00.92,Main,Law,0,0,0,,There's something\NI'd like to discuss with you, Straw-Hatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.43,0:22:07.21,Main,Law,0,0,0,,It may have been just a coincidence that you came to this island,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.81,0:22:15.04,Main,Law,0,0,0,,but there's actually a {\i1}key{\i0}{\fscx125} {\r}hidden here.  One with\Nthe power to throw the entire New World into chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.68,0:22:19.96,Main,Law,0,0,0,,There are two ways to survive in the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.15,0:22:25.63,Main,Law,0,0,0,,Either be protected by one of the Four Emperors,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.63,0:22:27.52,Main,Law,0,0,0,,or fight all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.53,0:22:34.58,Main,Law,0,0,0,,You're not the kind of guy\Nwho'll serve under someone else, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.25,0:22:38.16,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,That's right.  I prefer being the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.16,0:22:43.18,Main,Law,0,0,0,,Then, form an alliance with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.94,0:22:46.55,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,An alliance?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.55,0:22:50.68,Main,Law,0,0,0,,If you and I work together, we might be able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.32,0:23:01.19,Main,Law,0,0,0,,I've got a plan to dethrone one of the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.04,0:23:10.54,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Law wants to overthrow one of the Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.54,0:23:14.57,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The rest of the crew\Nis understandably shaken by this surprising plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.57,0:23:17.20,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,but Luffy's answer\Nis even more surprising to the crew...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.20,0:23:19.47,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,and Law himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.47,0:23:25.21,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,While this is happening,\NCaesar begins his most evil scheme of all time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.21,0:23:26.57,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.57,0:23:27.39,Main,Luffy+Title,0,0,0,,It's Formed!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.39,0:23:29.55,Main,Luffy+Title,0,0,0,,A Pirate Alliance between Luffy and Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.55,0:23:31.77,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
